metadata.instructions:
File naming rules: AWT_ MODIS_ FSC_ yyyymmdd. TIF, where
（1）AWT_ MODIS_ FSC: MODIS daily cloudless snow coverage product in Asian water tower area;
(2) Yyyymmdd: indicates the product time yyyy mm DD.
The file is in GeoTIFF format, which is supported by common remote sensing software ArcGIS, envi / IDL and MATLAB; The spatial reference is WGS84 datum plane and Equal latitude and longitude projection;
